I am able to reproduce this bug using Build id: 200406110010 on Mac OS 10.3.3.
This doesn't seem to happen on windows, but happens on the Mac everytime I do
the following:

- I happen to be running a fresh workspace (not sure if that matters or not)
- Resource Perspective (default)
- Go to "File->Import->External Plugins and Fragments"
- Uncheck the "Target Platform" box
- Select the plug-in location field and start typing random character
- Hit "Cancel"
